    <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1RenderEffect" kindref="compound">RenderEffect</ref> is an interface for visual effects. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Each effect has a single owner <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1View" kindref="compound">View</ref>.</para>
<para>Used internal at: <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1View_1aa4139cc500c68bb1b7fbdb4685aa1bd1" kindref="member">Ui::View::SetRenderEffect(Ui::RenderEffect effect)</ref>; <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1View_1ae6357827ea66e6f63e4251c10ff173ad" kindref="member">Ui::View::ClearRenderEffect()</ref>; <simplesect kind="note"><para><ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1RenderEffect" kindref="compound">RenderEffect</ref> is interface class without constructor. Create resource by subclass. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
